Interface CTemporal

All Superinterfaces:
ArchetypeConstraint, CDefinedObject, CObject, COrdered, CPrimitiveObject
All Known Subinterfaces:
CDate, CDateTime, CTime
public interface CTemporal extends COrdered
Purpose Abstract parent of `C_ORDERED` types whose base type is an ISO date/time type.
